No. 09-8638. Page Penk, Petitioner v. Edward Tauer, Mayor of the City of Aurora, Colorado, et al. 559 U.S. 1000, 130 S. Ct. 1898,

176 L. Ed. 2d 357,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2359. March 22, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Colorado dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
